## 📋 Vapi Configuration Steps

To connect your Vapi Voice Assistant to this application:

### 1. Webhook Setup
- Go to [Vapi Dashboard > Webhooks](https://dashboard.vapi.ai/webhooks).
- Click **Create Webhook** or edit your settings:
  - **Server URL**: `https://<your-vercel-domain>.vercel.app/api/vapi`
  - **Status**: Enabled.

### 2. Payload Format (Auto-Processed by `/api/vapi`)
Vapi dispatches the `end-of-call-report` event:
```json
{
  "message": {
    "type": "end-of-call-report",
    "call": {
      "id": "vapi-call-id",
      "transcript": "Hi, this is Dr. Sachin Shinde. I earn 2 Lakhs per month and I'm looking for a Doctor Loan of 25 Lakhs. My email is enquiry@avanifinserv.com.",
      "customer": {
        "number": "+919175635165"
      }
    },
    "analysis": {
      "structuredData": {
        "name": "Sachin Shinde",
        "email": "enquiry@avanifinserv.com",
        "loanType": "Doctor Loan",
        "loanAmount": 2500000,
        "monthlyIncome": 200000,
        "employmentType": "Doctor (Self-Employed)"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

